        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/176/139/original/838f73e1-12b3-4572-9166-ec879236ee07.png" srcset="" alt="Open Course Details" height="82" width="670">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_77BB9F20-028A-0135-BD9C-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Course Details</strong> tab.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="enable_grading_scheme" data-step-uuid="F06954C0-B758-4618-9D37-0B0C64394031">
    <h2 id="enable_grading_scheme" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Enable Grading Scheme</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/623/309/original/960c74ca-19f7-47af-ae79-a6a60a66caca.png" srcset="" alt="Enable Grading Scheme" height="43" width="381">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_77BBD390-028A-0135-BD9E-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Enable course grading scheme</strong> checkbox.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="set-grading-scheme" data-step-uuid="f7233714-543e-46e0-ae36-70398a111600">
    <h2 id="set-grading-scheme" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Set Grading Scheme</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/260/500/original/155fde9c-dbe2-4b92-a1cd-b5b2a75ae3cd.png" srcset="" alt="Set Grading Scheme" height="205" width="673">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_fca3f750-df72-4512-ac7b-e9e8bdced536" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To use a default grading scheme provided by your account, click the <strong>Grading Scheme </strong>drop-down menu [1] and select the grading scheme.</p>
<p>To <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-add-a-grading-scheme-in-a-course/ta-p/1054" target="_blank">create a grading scheme</a> for your course, click the <strong>Add New Grading Scheme</strong> button [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view_grading_scheme" data-step-uuid="3E94D6E0-2F57-4497-B8A3-11184FC87ABC">
