      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_77BC3670-028A-0135-BDA2-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Canvas displays the Default Canvas Grading Scheme. If you want to select another grading scheme, click the <strong>Grading Scheme </strong>drop-down menu [1] and select a Course Level or Account Level grading scheme [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

